article_id:1934,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia went live at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1611727200"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>What are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>・The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons is boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div>Newly added featured adventurer:</div><div>5★ Gala Chelle (shadow/rapid-fire manacaster)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia appearance rates:</div><div>5★ total: 6.00%</div><div>5★ featured total: 0.50% (Adventurers: 0.50%)</div><div>5★ standard total: 5.50% (Adventurers: 2.50%, Dragons: 3.00%)</div><div>4★ standard total: 16.00% (Adventurers: 8.55%, Dragons: 7.45%)</div><div>3★ standard total: 78.00% (Adventurers: 47.00%, Dragons: 31.00%)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1611727200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1612072799"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the newly added featured adventurer below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div>
