<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/ec6eab0a620c3865e404323b319f0abe2.png"></span><span>Radiant Scion II</span></dt><dd><div>When shapeshifting, Chelle will transform<br>into Cat Sìth regardless of what dragon she<br>is equipped with. In addition, using Burlone<br>Gatto will grant her the "Royal Pride" effect<br>for the remainder of the quest.<br>Royal Pride can stack up to 10 times, and<br>each stack reduces damage taken by 1%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/bd7de81c28d0b9c93b0edbfc86b0cb6a2.png"></span><span>Princess's Grace II</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to blindness<br>and paralysis by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/fd589517c61c65312e1509e13a36cd412.png"></span><span>Star of the Dance II</span></dt><dd><div>Increases force strike damage by 45%,<br>increases it up to an additional 30% based<br>on the number of buffs Chelle has, and,<br>when she has five or more Royal Pride<br>stacks, creates a buff zone around her<br>that reduces damage taken by 10%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities, and represent the adventurer at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div>・Adventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.</div><div><br></div><div>■Regarding Gala Chelle&#39;s Force Strike<br>Gala Chelle&#39;s force strike reduces the enemy&#39;s mode gauge to a greater extent than the standard force strike used by other rapid-fire manacaster adventurers.</div><div><br></div><div>Note: For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1611727200,update_time1611562811